286
00:14:39,470 --> 00:14:43,020
Welcome Mr. Liu, the commissioner of 5 provinces of north.

287
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:49,540
Mr. Liu.

288
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:52,580
We prepared a feast for you.

289
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,540
Please get off.

290
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:09,140
My surname is Wang.

291
00:15:09,470 --> 00:15:10,750
I’m the secretary of Commissioner Liu.

292
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:14,390
He asked me to tell you

293
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,310
and Commander Cao.

294
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,510
He said

295
00:15:18,230 --> 00:15:20,310
that he has a lot of work

296
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,270
and the days at here are numbered.

297
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:26,020
These red tapes are not necessary.

298
00:15:28,230 --> 00:15:29,950
Sorry that I didn’t arrange it well.

299
00:15:30,420 --> 00:15:32,270
Please forgive me.

300
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:35,220
Mr. Liu, could you please get off?

301
00:15:52,110 --> 00:15:53,870
Mr. Liu let me tell you

302
00:15:54,250 --> 00:15:55,990
that he’s inspecting secretly in this city.

303
00:15:56,890 --> 00:15:58,580
Anyone who

304
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:00,830
make troubles

305
00:16:01,470 --> 00:16:02,750
to stop his work

306
00:16:04,300 --> 00:16:06,340
will be executed with this Sword.

307
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:10,020
Mr. Cao, do you understand?

308
00:16:11,550 --> 00:16:13,460
Please tell Mr. Liu.

309
00:16:14,350 --> 00:16:17,340
I won’t forget what he said.

310
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,830
I’ll do my best to cooperate with him.

311
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,070
Go.

312
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:39,680
Thanks for your support.

313
00:16:39,690 --> 00:16:40,440
Thank you.

314
00:16:40,450 --> 00:16:41,090
Thank you.

315
00:16:41,770 --> 00:16:42,410
Thank you.

316
00:16:42,580 --> 00:16:43,850
Thank you.

317
00:16:46,860 --> 00:16:47,880
-Bravo!
-Please have a check.

318
00:16:47,890 --> 00:16:49,730
Boy, good performer.

319
00:16:50,250 --> 00:16:51,090
If you are lucky enough,

320
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:52,910
you may be a star one day.

321
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:54,060
Thank you.

322
00:16:55,330 --> 00:16:56,440
Boy.

323
00:16:58,500 --> 00:17:00,560
I’ll order an opera.

324
00:17:05,810 --> 00:17:08,319
You look familiar.

325
00:17:12,190 --> 00:17:13,700
Looking at the bruises on your face,

326
00:17:14,069 --> 00:17:16,180
I know you are Zhouzi.

327
00:17:17,190 --> 00:17:19,460
Aren’t you in Sixi’er’s theater?

328
00:17:20,230 --> 00:17:21,339
Why did you come here?

329
00:17:21,589 --> 00:17:24,300
Mr. Zheng, why are you here?

330
00:17:25,349 --> 00:17:26,990
Strange words.

331
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,870
In Peking,

332
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:31,700
is some place where I daren’t go?

333
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,100
What?

334
00:17:35,230 --> 00:17:36,630
What are you doing here?

335
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:39,870
Perform for debts.

336
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:43,460
Were you driven out by Sixi’er?

337
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:48,100
Now that you perform on the street,

338
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:50,990
I’ll order one.

339
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:54,420
Sixi’er can’t teach you others,

340
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,100
but he’s best at

341
00:17:57,380 --> 00:17:59,420
the vulgar opera.

342
00:18:03,070 --> 00:18:03,670
I...

343
00:18:05,950 --> 00:18:07,460
Am I so mean?

344
00:18:07,470 --> 00:18:08,390
Am I?

345
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:14,790
I’ll order Make a Scene in the Chamber.

346
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:16,300
Sing for me.

347
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:21,510
I can’t.

348
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:26,820
You can’t or you won’t?

349
00:18:27,950 --> 00:18:29,390
Mr. Zheng, he’s still young.

350
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,270
Go away.

351
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:32,490
Go.

352
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:37,670
He doesn’t accept my order.

353
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:39,670
Does he look down on me?

354
00:18:41,470 --> 00:18:43,510
Mr. Zheng, please be merciful.

355
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:47,940
Will you sing?

356
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,270
With so much money,

357
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,150
you can invite a star to perform.

358
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:58,910
Seems that you want to be hit.

359
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:01,060
Guys,

360
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:03,870
hit him!

361
00:19:14,560 --> 00:19:16,060
You did very well.

362
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:19,550
Performers don’t accept

363
00:19:20,190 --> 00:19:23,300
any requirement casually.

364
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:38,910
Don’t come,

365
00:19:39,670 --> 00:19:43,460
or I’ll ask my dad to kill you.

366
00:19:43,840 --> 00:19:44,510
Jiang Dengbao.

367
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:47,030
With the protection of your dad,

368
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:49,870
you bully the weak people all the time.

369
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,550
If you don’t stop your sin,

370
00:19:51,710 --> 00:19:52,990
you’ll get punishment.

371
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:54,300
Then even your dad can’t protect you.

372
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:57,460
Nonsense.

373
00:19:57,680 --> 00:19:59,550
Don’t spread rumors.

374
00:19:59,710 --> 00:20:02,060
How did you get your third concubine?

375
00:20:02,430 --> 00:20:03,700
How was the leader of Qingyin Theater

376
00:20:03,710 --> 00:20:05,300
put in the prison?

377
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:06,750
There are people remembering those.

378
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:14,550
Shang, don’t go.

379
00:20:15,430 --> 00:20:16,990
Wait for me here.

380
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:33,910
Are you all right?

381
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:35,390
I’m all right.

382
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:36,820
But I brought you trouble again.

383
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:41,030
Mr. Shang. Did you...

384
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:44,510
Ask me whatever you want.

385
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:47,870
Did... Did you leave me on purpose?

386
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:50,460
I

387
00:20:50,470 --> 00:20:52,460
want to cure your “fright disease”.

388
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:54,530
If I made you uncomfortable,

389
00:20:54,950 --> 00:20:55,990
I apologize to you.

390
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:57,510
No, no, no.

391
00:20:58,710 --> 00:21:00,390
You helped me.

392
00:21:00,560 --> 00:21:01,910
I should thank you.

393
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:04,790
Are you still afraid of crowd of people?

394
00:21:09,180 --> 00:21:09,930
Good.

395
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:13,120
After lunch,

396
00:21:13,780 --> 00:21:15,360
let’s buy clothes.

397
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:16,530
Go.

398
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:21,620
(The world belongs to people Peking Government
Peking Social Affairs Bureau Peking Land Bureau)

399
00:21:21,940 --> 00:21:23,240
Our men in Nanking

400
00:21:23,730 --> 00:21:25,170
get the report

401
00:21:26,150 --> 00:21:29,120
that firearms are transferred in Peking.

402
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:32,080
The smugglers are rampant.

403
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:33,840
They are

404
00:21:33,850 --> 00:21:36,570
even protected by the army.

405
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:38,530
How...

406
00:21:40,090 --> 00:21:41,240
How can it be possible?

407
00:21:42,060 --> 00:21:43,360
What strange news.

408
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:45,530
Now the war is in process.

409
00:21:45,820 --> 00:21:47,600
The relationship between China and Japan is tense.

410
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:49,770
How come they do such a thing

411
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:50,960
instead of fighting the battle?

412
00:21:52,700 --> 00:21:53,720
Mr. Jiang

413
00:21:53,730 --> 00:21:55,600
appointed me to come to

414
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,390
investigate this thing

415
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:00,960
and inspect the livelihood.

416
00:22:06,540 --> 00:22:07,600
I read

417
00:22:08,580 --> 00:22:09,480
these archives.

418
00:22:10,610 --> 00:22:12,290
I also wandered in the city.

419
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:14,410
The economy is developed well.

420
00:22:15,580 --> 00:22:18,080
All walks of life work together.

421
00:22:18,610 --> 00:22:20,170
But the security is not as good as the economy.

422
00:22:22,330 --> 00:22:25,690
The urban is peaceful

423
00:22:27,010 --> 00:22:28,570
but the suburb is under chaos.

424
00:22:29,830 --> 00:22:31,450
There are too many bandits.

425
00:22:32,890 --> 00:22:36,080
On my way here, I met several bandits.

426
00:22:36,700 --> 00:22:38,840
They kidnap and blackmail people.

427
00:22:39,270 --> 00:22:41,830
Who can make sure

428
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:43,650
that people in Peking are safe?

429
00:22:43,850 --> 00:22:45,640
So...

430
00:22:45,830 --> 00:22:47,420
Were you in danger?

431
00:22:48,190 --> 00:22:49,150
Yes.

432
00:22:52,280 --> 00:22:53,580
If I was in danger,

433
00:22:53,590 --> 00:22:55,150
how can you see me now?

434
00:22:56,760 --> 00:22:57,670
Yes.

435
00:22:57,800 --> 00:23:00,870
Luckily, the warriors are all brave and strong.

436
00:23:01,430 --> 00:23:03,340
The bandits got nothing from me.

437
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:05,510
The most of them were killed by my men,

438
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:07,030
and also, we caught some captives.

439
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:10,550
What a contribution.

440
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:13,270
Arrange a trial

441
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:16,270
to sentence these bandits.

442
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:18,340
First, it’s to calm the public.

443
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:21,180
Second, it’s to deter the gangsters.

444
00:23:22,190 --> 00:23:25,300
Don’t worry. Let me take care of it.

445
00:23:32,300 --> 00:23:33,100
Mr. Cheng.

446
00:23:34,830 --> 00:23:36,220
Mr. Cao always behaves like this.

447
00:23:36,230 --> 00:23:37,420
He won’t stop

448
00:23:37,430 --> 00:23:38,270
until he thinks it’s enough.

449
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:40,390
Mr. Cheng. Please wait him in the room.

450
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,790
Mr. Cheng, you...

451
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:04,220
Did Liu Hanyun take action?

452
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:07,300
My storage has been sealed up.

453
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:10,270
Don’t you still have some hidden warehouses?

454
00:24:10,710 --> 00:24:12,990
These will be sealed up sooner or later.

455
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:15,700
I come to ask you

456
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:18,060
whether you can move

457
00:24:18,230 --> 00:24:19,870
my firearm in the hidden warehouses.

458
00:24:21,560 --> 00:24:22,750
Ask Commander Cao.

459
00:24:23,110 --> 00:24:24,460
How can I achieve it?

460
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:26,180
He is recuperating.

461
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:28,510
Kimura doesn’t let others see him.

462
00:24:29,280 --> 00:24:31,510
Also, we have nothing to say.

463
00:24:32,110 --> 00:24:34,460
The Japanese doctor is like a supervisor.

464
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:36,100
What can I talk to him

465
00:24:36,110 --> 00:24:37,180
in front of Japanese?

466
00:24:38,070 --> 00:24:40,790
Then give some gifts to Mr. Liu.

467
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,270
You are best at that.

468
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:45,420
He doesn’t appear in public,

469
00:24:45,830 --> 00:24:47,420
so I don’t even have a chance.

470
00:24:48,190 --> 00:24:50,390
You’ve run out of your ways.

471
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:52,180
And I become your last hope?

472
00:24:58,430 --> 00:25:00,060
Don’t laugh at me.

473
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:03,820
Do you think you are not involved?

474
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,510
Once they know it’s me,

475
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,940
your whole Family

476
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:10,270
can’t get away

477
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:12,420
from it.

478
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:17,390
These firearms are strongest evidence.

479
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:20,100
Uncle, don’t worry.

480
00:25:20,470 --> 00:25:21,220
Well...

481
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:22,940
I’ll talk to my father.

482
00:25:23,230 --> 00:25:24,820
Calm down.

483
00:25:24,830 --> 00:25:26,510
Pray to the god.

484
00:25:26,590 --> 00:25:28,180
Don’t leave any clue of your warehouses

485
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:29,940
to Liu Hanyun.

486
00:25:43,110 --> 00:25:43,630
Sir,

487
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:44,940
everything goes well.

488
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,100
Have a rest.

489
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:56,910
The commander is resting. Please go back.

490
00:25:57,680 --> 00:25:59,220
I come to see my father.

491
00:25:59,560 --> 00:26:01,060
You don’t have right to stop me.

492
00:26:02,280 --> 00:26:03,550
Let him in.

493
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:19,700
Prat. What are you doing here?

494
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:22,180
Are you here to check if I’m still alive?

495
00:26:22,470 --> 00:26:24,630
I come to chat with you.

496
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:26,820
About what?

497
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:30,940
With a woman around us,

498
00:26:30,950 --> 00:26:32,150
I’m not convenient to say casually.

499
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,510
How about having a bath with me?

500
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:42,820
Can he do it?

501
00:26:44,890 --> 00:26:46,270
The commander is weak now,

502
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:48,030
so having a bath for a long time is not good.

503
00:26:48,430 --> 00:26:49,990
I must be with him.

504
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:52,390
You are with him when he’s having a bath?

505
00:26:52,760 --> 00:26:53,460
Alright.

506
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:55,510
I’ve been resting for several days.

507
00:26:56,290 --> 00:26:57,750
I got sweaty.

508
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:01,030
Scrub for me.

509
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,990
OK, no problem.

510
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:15,820
Fujin, I come to give you tickets.

511
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:19,460
Mr. Shang, you are here.

512
00:27:21,850 --> 00:27:22,910
Godfather, you...

513
00:27:23,560 --> 00:27:25,630
Let me help you.

514
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:28,220
Fujin,

515
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:30,100
have a good rest.

516
00:27:30,710 --> 00:27:33,300
I’ll visit you as possible as I can.

517
00:27:37,110 --> 00:27:38,580
Godfather, why are you here?

518
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,150
Let’s talk about it outside.

519
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:47,300
(Best wishes for Fujin)

520
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:03,150
Godfather,

521
00:28:03,310 --> 00:28:06,030
I didn’t think you and Fujin are friends.

522
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:08,940
Yes.

523
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:13,280
When I succeeded in the government examination,

524
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:15,580
Prince An was my master.

525
00:28:16,440 --> 00:28:17,940
And when I became an official,

526
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:20,030
he was my leader.

527
00:28:21,470 --> 00:28:22,940
In Peking,

528
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:24,460
Prince An and Fujin

529
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:27,220
took care of me for these years.

530
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:28,960
So once I arrived in Peking,

531
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:30,750
I came to visit her.

532
00:28:32,950 --> 00:28:33,940
But I didn’t think

533
00:28:35,130 --> 00:28:37,180
she can’t recognize me

534
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:39,230
due to her disease.

535
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:40,550
Godfather,

536
00:28:41,110 --> 00:28:42,820
you were an official of Qing?

537
00:28:45,430 --> 00:28:46,150
Yes.

538
00:28:46,630 --> 00:28:48,360
Can you tell me your life during that period?

539
00:28:49,010 --> 00:28:50,060
To tell you the truth,

540
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:52,060
my new play

541
00:28:52,230 --> 00:28:54,270
is a story in the palace.

542
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:58,270
Really? Tell me

543
00:28:58,560 --> 00:28:59,870
what the story it is.

544
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:03,160
In this story...

545
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:08,910
Cao Guixiu,

546
00:29:09,710 --> 00:29:10,790
you are a jerk!

547
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:12,910
How dare you blackmail me?

548
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:15,060
Your position and uniform

549
00:29:15,070 --> 00:29:16,340
are given by me.

550
00:29:16,950 --> 00:29:18,700
What? Now you’ve grown up,

551
00:29:18,710 --> 00:29:20,220
and interfere my thing?

552
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:21,790
Get lost.

553
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:23,910
OK, don’t regret!

554
00:29:24,230 --> 00:29:25,750
My most regretful thing

555
00:29:25,760 --> 00:29:27,060
is having you.

556
00:29:27,540 --> 00:29:28,220
Get out!

557
00:29:46,470 --> 00:29:47,340
Everything is ready.

558
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,420
Mr. Cheng.

559
00:29:53,430 --> 00:29:54,420
Where is your leader?

560
00:29:54,870 --> 00:29:57,150
He went to give Fujin tickets.

561
00:29:58,850 --> 00:29:59,810
Give whom?

562
00:30:01,060 --> 00:30:02,050
Fujin.

563
00:30:06,300 --> 00:30:08,280
Godfather, don’t forget

564
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:10,220
to watch my new play tomorrow.

565
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:11,320
I promise.

566
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:13,050
I must go to watch you.

567
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,480
Godfather, take care.

568
00:30:34,460 --> 00:30:35,200
Mr. Cheng.

569
00:30:36,330 --> 00:30:37,570
Who is that?

570
00:30:37,580 --> 00:30:38,480
What pomp.

571
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:40,360
My godfather, Liu Hanyun.

572
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:45,450
Mr. Cheng.

573
